title: Sample Book (France), 1937
description: Sample book containing fabrics by Rodier. White cover with "Rodier" in large printed red and black letters. Contains fourteen fashion sketches and fabric samples: 220 wool, 11 silk, 6 printed silk, two metallic, and one silk embroidered with metallic thread.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (France), 1937. cardboard binding, wool, silk, metallic. Gift of William Hardy, Inc.. 1939-26-1.
